      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Leverage Copilot\n\nChat with the **live n8n backlog**. Vector search (issues + PRs) + ranking tables + **comment deep-dive**.\n\n**Demo:**\n- Why is #14361 ranked first?\n- Deep dive #14361 \u2014 what are maintainers saying?\n- What MCP issues hurt most?\n- code_scout: McpTrigger",
